<h1>Articles!</h1>

<ol>
<% @articles.each do |article| %>
  <li><%= link_to article.title, article %></li>
<% end %>
</ol>

<p>
  The following button will generate a new article with a bunch of negative comments. Just a single downvote on them will be enough to tip the scales, and slice them out of the discourse.
</p>
<%= button_to "Generate demo article", seed_articles_url, method: "POST" %>
